@startuml erd_supabase
!include _thesis_style.puml

' ============================================================
' Production-grade ERD for the Supabase (PostgreSQL) backend.
' Grounded in smart_city_reporter_app/supabase/schema.sql.
' Covers: laporan, prediksi multiclass, assignment instansi
' terdekat, bukti penyelesaian, dan kebijakan RLS per peran.
' ============================================================

' --- local refinements (scoped to this diagram only) ---
hide circle
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam nodesep 28
skinparam ranksep 48
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FEF9E7
  BorderColor #B7950B
  FontColor #5B4A06
}
skinparam legendBackgroundColor #F8F9F9
skinparam legendBorderColor #2E4053

' ===================== ENTITIES =====================

entity "auth.users\n<<Supabase Auth>>" as Users #F4F6F7 {
  * id : uuid <<PK>>
  --
  email : text
  created_at : timestamptz
}

entity "profiles" as Profiles #EBF5FB {
  * id : uuid <<PK, FK auth.users>>
  --
  * full_name : text
  * email : text <<unique>>
  * phone_number : text
  profile_photo_url : text
  * is_moderator : boolean = false
  * role : user_role = citizen
  assigned_agency : issue_category
  * created_at : timestamptz
  * updated_at : timestamptz
  --
  CHECK: role = agency_admin => assigned_agency NOT NULL
}

entity "reports" as Reports {
  * id : uuid <<PK>>
  .. Identitas & Lokasi ..
  * user_id : uuid <<FK profiles>>
  * reporter_name : text
  * reporter_email : text
  * image_url : text
  * description : text
  * latitude : double precision
  * longitude : double precision
  * address : text
  .. Klasifikasi & Prediksi AI ..
  * category : issue_category
  * ai_prediction : text
  * ai_confidence : numeric(5,4)
  * ai_probabilities : jsonb
  ai_model_name : text
  ai_model_version : text
  .. Assignment Instansi Terdekat ..
  assigned_agency_id : text
  assigned_agency_name : text
  assigned_agency_category : issue_category
  assigned_distance_meters : double precision
  routing_method : text
  .. Status & Verifikasi ..
  * status : report_status = submitted
  verified_by : uuid <<FK profiles>>
  verified_at : timestamptz
  rejection_reason : text
  .. Bukti Penyelesaian ..
  resolution_evidence_photo_url : text
  resolution_note : text
  resolved_by : uuid <<FK profiles>>
  resolved_at : timestamptz
  .. Audit Waktu ..
  * created_at : timestamptz
  * updated_at : timestamptz
}

entity "report_history" as History #F5EEF8 {
  * id : uuid <<PK>>
  --
  * report_id : uuid <<FK reports>>
  * status : report_status
  * note : text
  updated_by : uuid <<FK profiles>>
  * created_at : timestamptz
}

entity "storage.objects\n<<bucket>> report-images (public)" as ReportImages #EAFAF1 {
  * name : text <<path>>
  --
  path: {user_id}/<berkas>
  image_url
  resolution_evidence_photo_url
}

entity "storage.objects\n<<bucket>> profile-photos (public)" as ProfilePhotos #EAFAF1 {
  * name : text <<path>>
  --
  path: {user_id}/<berkas>
  profile_photo_url
}

' ===================== RELATIONSHIPS =====================

Users ||--|| Profiles : "id (1:1)"
note on link
**trigger** handle_new_user()
membuat baris profiles saat pendaftaran
end note

Profiles ||--o{ Reports : "user_id  «pelapor»"
Profiles ||--o{ Reports : "verified_by / resolved_by  «operator»"
Profiles ||--o{ History  : "updated_by"
Reports  ||--o{ History  : "report_id"
Reports  ||..o{ ReportImages  : "URL (logis)"
Profiles ||..o{ ProfilePhotos : "URL (logis)"

' ===================== RLS / POLICY NOTES =====================

note left of Profiles
**RLS - profiles**
**SELECT / UPDATE**: diri sendiri atau moderator
**INSERT**: diri sendiri (auth.uid() = id)
end note

note right of Reports
**RLS - reports : kebijakan per peran**
**SELECT**: semua pengguna terautentikasi
**INSERT**: pemilik (auth.uid() = user_id)
**UPDATE** (reports_update_scoped):
* Warga -> laporan miliknya
* agency_admin -> category = assigned_agency
* super_admin -> semua + reassign kategori
end note

note bottom of History
**RLS - report_history**
**SELECT**: semua terautentikasi
**INSERT** (history_insert_scoped):
updated_by = auth.uid() dan
(admin atau pemilik laporan)
end note

note bottom of Reports
**RPC update_report_status()  -  security invoker**
Memperbarui reports + menyisipkan report_history
dalam satu transaksi. Menegakkan:
* agency_admin hanya laporan instansinya
* hanya super_admin boleh reassign kategori
* status 'resolved' wajib foto bukti penyelesaian
end note

' ===================== ENUM CATALOG =====================

note as N_enum #F8F9F9
**Tipe enum PostgreSQL**
**issue_category** (9): dinas_bina_marga, satpol_pp, dinas_perhubungan,
kelurahan, dinas_pertamanan_hutan, dinas_sda, dinas_cipta_karya,
badan_bumd, instansi_lain
**report_status** (5): submitted -> verified -> in_progress -> resolved / rejected
**user_role** (3): citizen, agency_admin, super_admin
end note

legend right
|= Notasi |= Arti |
| * kolom | wajib (NOT NULL) |
| PK / FK | primary / foreign key |
| crow's foot | relasi satu-ke-banyak |
| garis putus-putus | tautan URL (bukan FK fisik) |
endlegend

@enduml
